_sText: (MAP UPDATED AND FIXED) ### This is a simple and short surf map, there's only one stage, and after 5 mins the players are teleported to a combat+strafing jail. ### Inspired by my personal Salvia Divinorum experiences, this map shows a little of what I felt and saw during my visions. #### If yall find a bug/error, please tell me so I can fix it :) ##### NOTE: This map is very dark. A high brightness level is required. Video
